{"tid":1646103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「行動」","createTime":"2019-10-11T07:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T07:29:24.000Z","uid":201112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"083fb1da166132b0f9041e011e902a8cb58d87c9","tid":1646103,"uid":201112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T07:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ComprkJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FComprkJ.jpg&h=9dedc275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家都覺得開埋呢啲post做乜鳩，但係大家可唔可以睇下呢一刻嘅連登發生緊咩事？熱門post全L部都無個係講聽日會點，今日呢一刻中環係點。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話要唔理手足呀！但我想係啲post可唔可以集中啲。浮屍事件3個post，性侵事件3，4個，中大校長又幾個，林肯大學呢個咁嘅死人嘢都唔知po嚟做咩？<br />\n<br />\n另外，都有其他post講過話活動會唔會太密？都希望大家係討論問題，呢一刻我地要點做？唔係等人叫你先做呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">裝備</span></span><br />\n全世界入黎推爆佢 唔推都要入黎睇一睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">後日</span></span><br />\n【行動post】星期日再度各區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641015</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【遍地再開花】香港人報仇！星期日 14:00 十八區再開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644618</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明日</span></span><br />\n入嚟傾下星期六點！tst 有兩個遊行係咪搞笑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1645829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1645829</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚</span></span><br />\n對抗警暴，1011 十八區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"138af862190dd5a506f96a415bb47cc3e71